Guile-RPC
=========

This package provides a pure Scheme implementation of XDR and ONC RPC
(respectively RFC 4506 and RFC 1831) for GNU Guile 1.8.


Requirements
------------

GNU Guile 1.8.x or later
guile-r6rs-libs 0.0 or later


Development
-----------

The main GNU Arch repository is currently located at
http://www.laas.fr/~lcourtes/software/arch-2006/ .  Look for branch
`guile-rpc--devo--0'.

Please email me, Ludovic Courtès <ludovic.courtes@laas.fr>, for
comments, patches, etc.


Enjoy!

Ludovic, February 2007.
